{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Create your own cozy forest!</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Plant Seeds and Watch Them Grow</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/tree_grow_3.gif?t=1737559226\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the full lifecycle of trees: seed, sapling, adult tree, dead tree and fallen trunk. Each step creates a different habitat for other plants and animals.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fill Your Forest with Animals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/habitats_2.gif?t=1737559226\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each animal has specific habitat needs you have to fullfill before adding them. Squirrels need trees, butterflies need flowers etc.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Click Animals to Make Them Poop and More</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/click_poop_2.gif?t=1737559226\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clicking on animals trigger different behaviors that influence the forest ecosystem: Moose poop, fertilizing the soil. Voles eat tree roots, damaging the tree. Foxes hunt other animals.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Adapt to the Terrain or Terraform It to Your Needs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/different_landscapes.gif?t=1737559226\" />Create forests in diverse terrains including hills, lakes, mountains, fjords and wetlands. Terraform the terrain if you want even more control.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Survive Natural Disasters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/wildfires_store_page.gif?t=1737559226\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forest fires, storms and bark beetle swarms affect the forest in various ways. Can you use them to your advantage and create a thriving ecosystem?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737559226","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737559226","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737559226","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737559226","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2968160,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Create your own cozy forest!</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Plant Seeds and Watch Them Grow</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/tree_grow_3.gif?t=1737559226\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the full lifecycle of trees: seed, sapling, adult tree, dead tree and fallen trunk. Each step creates a different habitat for other plants and animals.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fill Your Forest with Animals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2718240/extras/habitats_2.gif?t=1737559226\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each animal has specific habitat needs you have to fullfill before adding them. Squirrels need trees, butterflies need flowers etc.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Click Animals to Make Them Poop and More</strong></h2><p c